            <td>pixel.wp.com</td>
            <td>&mdash;</td>
            <td>pixel_tracker</td>
            <td>Session</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>Contact form and CRM cookies (HubSpot)</h3>
      <p>We use HubSpot to manage contact form submissions and customer relationship data. HubSpot places cookies on your device when you visit our site, including cookies that track your browsing session and associate it with any form submission you make.</p>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Cookie</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Provider</th><th>Service</th><th>Type</th><th>Expires</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><code>hubspotutk</code></td>
            <td>Tracks a visitor's identity across sessions for deduplication of contacts</td>
            <td>.zachbeauvais.com</td>
            <td><a href="https://legal.hubspot.com/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HubSpot</a></td>
            <td>http_cookie</td>
            <td>180 days</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><code>__hstc</code></td>
            <td>Main tracking cookie; includes timestamp of first visit, last visit, and current session</td>
            <td>.zachbeauvais.com</td>
